    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and not assessed, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements for a Class II device at MRL 2. Mesh convergence, pressure-flow validation, and hemolysis scalar transport validation provide converging lines of evidence that the CFD model is fit for purpose in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all five operating points. Assessment team accepts the model for the stated context of use.",
